{{校对翻译}}
'''Windows系统评估工具'''（{{lang-en|Windows System Assessment Tool}}，简称'''WinSAT'''）是[[微软|微软]][[Windows_Vista|Windows Vista]]、[[Windows_7|Windows 7]]和[[Windows_8|Windows 8]]中的一个模块，可以在[[控制面板|控制面板]]的性能信息和工具中找到（[[Windows_8.1|Windows 8.1]]中除外）。此工具可以测量当前运行硬件的各项特征和能力，然后将其报告为'''Windows体验指数'''（{{lang-en|Windows Experience Index}}，简称'''WEI'''）得分。体验指数包括五项子分数：处理器、内存、2D图形、3D图形和磁盘。最终的体验指数得分是分数最低的子分数，而'''不是'''五个子分数的平均值。<ref name="Softpedia">{{Cite web|url=http://news.softpedia.com/news/Windows-7-WEI-Scores-6-0-through-7-9-Explained-172277.shtml|title=Windows 7 WEI Scores 6.0 through 7.9 Explained|accessdate=June 3, 2011|publisher=Softpedia|archive-date=2017-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170817204059/http://news.softpedia.com/news/Windows-7-WEI-Scores-6-0-through-7-9-Explained-172277.shtml}}</ref><ref name="Microsoft_Perfect_Score">{{Cite web|url=http://windows.microsoft.com/en-gb/windows7/achieving-a-perfect-windows-experience-index-score-in-windows-7|title=Earning the top Windows Experience Index score|accessdate=June 3, 2011|publisher=Microsoft|archive-date=2016-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160620033020/http://windows.microsoft.com/en-gb/windows7/achieving-a-perfect-windows-experience-index-score-in-windows-7}}</ref>Windows Vista中的WinSAT将体验指数报告为一个从1.0至5.9的得分，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://windowsvistablog.com/blogs/windowsvista/archive/2006/09/22/windows-experience-index-an-in-depth-look.aspx |title=Vista Team Blog : Windows Experience Index: An In-Depth Look |accessdate=2016-06-16 |archive-date=2006-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061110165619/http://windowsvistablog.com/blogs/windowsvista/archive/2006/09/22/windows-experience-index-an-in-depth-look.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>Windows 7中上限增至7.9<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/239713/how_to_max_out_your_windows_performance_for_1000.html|title=How to Max Out Your Windows Performance for $1000|accessdate=May 17, 2014|author=Marco Chiappetta|date=September 8, 2011|publisher=[[PC_World|PC World]]|archive-date=2021-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427091819/https://www.pcworld.com/article/239713/how_to_max_out_your_windows_performance_for_1000.html}}</ref>Windows 8中增至9.9。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/hardware/hh825488.aspx|title=WinSAT Comprehensive|accessdate=May 17, 2014|date=October 20, 2013|publisher=MSDN|archive-date=2017-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170705090349/https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/hardware/hh825488.aspx}}</ref>

体验指数可以匹配用户的计算机硬件性能与软件的性能需求。例如，[[Windows_Aero|Aero]]图形界面在该指数小于3分时将不会自动启用。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://answers.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/forum/windows_7-desktop/full-screen-previews-have-got-disabled-how-do-i-re/d44193c0-7e51-4a2f-8ec0-4ac115c710c0|title=Full screen previews have got disabled. How do I re-enable them?|accessdate=June 3, 2011|publisher=Microsoft|archive-date=2011-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110728125642/http://answers.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/forum/windows_7-desktop/full-screen-previews-have-got-disabled-how-do-i-re/d44193c0-7e51-4a2f-8ec0-4ac115c710c0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://windows.microsoft.com/en-US/windows-vista/What-is-the-Windows-Experience-Index|title=What Is the Windows Experience Index|accessdate=June 3, 2011|publisher=Microsoft|archive-date=2013-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130707110430/http://windows.microsoft.com/en-US/windows-vista/What-is-the-Windows-Experience-Index}}</ref>

体验指数也可以揭示升级系统的哪个部分能得到最大的体验提升。例如，如果计算机的最低子分数是内存，升级[[随机存取存储器|内存]]一般会比升级硬盘或其他任何组件获得更大提升。<ref name="Microsoft_Perfect_Score">{{Cite web|url=http://windows.microsoft.com/en-gb/windows7/achieving-a-perfect-windows-experience-index-score-in-windows-7|title=Earning the top Windows Experience Index score|accessdate=June 3, 2011|publisher=Microsoft}}</ref>

详细的原始信息（例如实际的磁盘带宽）可以从命令行调用<code>winsat</code>获取。这也允许重新运行特定测试。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://windowsitpro.com/systems-management/winsat-command-line-utility |title=Winsat Command-Line Utility |access-date=2016-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160614173604/http://windowsitpro.com/systems-management/winsat-command-line-utility |archive-date=2016-06-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 从命令行获取体验指数得分应使用<code>winsat formal</code>，这也会更新<code>%systemroot%\Performance\WinSAT\DataStore</code>中存储的值。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://windowsitpro.com/systems-management/how-can-i-run-windows-system-assessment-tool-winsat-update-directly-command-line |title=How can I run the Windows System Assessment Tool (WinSAT) update directly from a command line? |access-date=2016-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611205033/http://windowsitpro.com/systems-management/how-can-i-run-windows-system-assessment-tool-winsat-update-directly-command-line |archive-date=2016-06-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>（里面存储的XML文件可以被轻易地手动修改以伪造性能报告值<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.howtogeek.com/71500/stupid-geek-tricks-hacking-the-windows-experience-index/ |title=Stupid Geek Tricks: Hacking the Windows Experience Index |access-date=2016-06-16 |archive-date=2021-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119111225/https://www.howtogeek.com/71500/stupid-geek-tricks-hacking-the-windows-experience-index/ }}</ref>）。体验指数也可被应用程序使用[[应用程序接口|API]]调用，应用程序可以根据硬件性能调用适当的函数，避免功能慢的难以接受。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/cc507870.aspx|title=Windows Experience Index: Overview|accessdate=September 24, 2011|publisher=Microsoft TechNet|archive-date=2017-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170818004622/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/cc507870.aspx}}</ref>

Windows体验指数在[[Windows_8.1|Windows 8.1]]中不会显示，因为WinSAT的[[图形用户界面|图形用户界面]]在此Windows版本中已被移除，不过[[命令行界面|命令行]]版本的winsat工具仍然存在并可正常运行。<ref name="WEI killed">{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnet.com/how-to/find-your-windows-experience-index-scores-in-windows-8-1/|title=Find your Windows Experience Index scores in Windows 8.1|accessdate=May 17, 2014|author=Ed Rhee|date=January 2, 2014|publisher=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506225236/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/find-your-windows-experience-index-scores-in-windows-8-1/}}</ref>根据{{tsl|en|PC_Pro|PC Pro}}的文章，微软移除WinSAT界面是为促进各种硬件都可顺畅运行Windows 8的想法。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcpro.co.uk/blogs/2013/09/19/farewell-to-the-windows-experience-index/|title=Farewell to the Windows Experience Index|accessdate=May 17, 2014|author=Darien Graham-Smith|date=September 19, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150514124635/http://www.pcpro.co.uk/blogs/2013/09/19/farewell-to-the-windows-experience-index|archive-date=2015-05-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
在2003年的[[游戏开发者大会|Game Developers Conference]]上，微软的Windows图形和游戏总经理Dean Lester在[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]的采访中指出，微软打算在Windows的下一版本（代号“Longhorn”，后来的[[Windows_Vista|Windows Vista]]）中将改善PC游戏体验作为新游戏倡议的一部分。莱斯特表示，这项倡议的一部分是操作系统将包含一个[[Games_for_Windows|游戏文件夹以集中化游戏的设置]]，以及其他功能，[[Windows_Display_Driver_Model|显卡驱动的精简]]、{{tsl|en|Security_and_safety_features_new_to_Windows_Vista#Parental_controls|游戏的家长控制}}和在安装时[[Games_for_Windows|可以直接从光盘启动Windows游戏]]——类似[[電子遊戲機|電子遊戲機]]的设计方式。微软还想要求在适用于Windows游戏的零售包装上使用新的系统需求说明系统，使用一个数字评分分类需求。<ref name="GDC">{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/microsofts-big-pc-plans/1100-2912498/|title=Microsoft's big PC plans|accessdate=August 10, 2015|date=March 10, 2003|last=Parker|first=Sam|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|archive-date=2019-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190218102525/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/microsofts-big-pc-plans/1100-2912498/}}</ref>在2004年，Lester说明微软想进一步扩展与硬件厂商的合作，使用一个“级别系统”标定系统硬件的性能和功能，创建适用于Windows Vista的PC，以及[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]外围设备将会与操作系统完全兼容。<ref name="LonghornXbox">{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/microsoft-talks-longhorn-xna-and-xbox-2/1100-6108247/|title=Microsoft talks Longhorn, XNA, and Xbox 2|accessdate=April 18, 2015|author=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=September 22, 2004|archive-date=2015-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150202112359/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/microsoft-talks-longhorn-xna-and-xbox-2/1100-6108247/|dead-url=no}}</ref>Windows Vista中的Windows体验指数依赖于WinSAT的测量结果，它可以提供准确的评估系统的能力——这些评级表示系统的能力，较高的得分表示更好的性能。

微软的Robert Stein在2004年建议的初步设计元素是，WinSAT计划在[[开箱体验|开箱体验]]时评估用户的硬件；<ref name="Stein">{{Cite web|url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/rs3art/304021764/in/set-72157594393542938|title=Aurora for OOBE|accessdate=April 18, 2015|date=November 22, 2006|last=Stein|first=Robert|work=[[Flickr|Flickr]]|archive-date=2016-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161111111248/https://www.flickr.com/photos/rs3art/304021764/in/set-72157594393542938}}</ref>这是一个设计决定，这是一个操作系统为[[軟件版本週期|发布到制造商]]保留的设计决定。<ref name="WinSAT2006">{{Cite web|url=http://download.microsoft.com/download/5/b/9/5b97017b-e28a-4bae-ba48-174cf47d23cd/cpa101_wh06.ppt|title=Windows Vista System Requirements and WinSAT|accessdate=April 18, 2015|date=2006|last=Russell|first=Richard|format=PPT|publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|archive-date=2022-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412004009/https://download.microsoft.com/download/5/b/9/5b97017b-e28a-4bae-ba48-174cf47d23cd/cpa101_wh06.ppt}}</ref>

在2005年[[WinHEC|Windows硬件工程会议]]期间，微软正式发布WinSAT，并提出这是一项不仅适用于游戏的技术，比如Windows Vista可以基于机器性能决定是否启用{{tsl|en|Compositing_window_manager|桌面合成}}。<ref name="LongShort">{{Cite web|url=http://www.techrepublic.com/article/the-long-and-short-of-longhorns-hardware-requirements/|title=The long and short of Longhorn's hardware requirements|accessdate=April 18, 2015|date=June 30, 2005|last=Shultz|first=Greg|work=[[TechRepublic|TechRepublic]]|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|archive-date=2017-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415131242/http://www.techrepublic.com/article/the-long-and-short-of-longhorns-hardware-requirements/}}</ref><ref name="Muench">{{Cite web|url=http://blogs.msdn.com/b/mikehall/archive/2005/04/26/412402.aspx|title=WinHEC : Chris Muench Report for Day 2 - Everything has two sides|accessdate=April 18, 2015|date=April 26, 2005|last=Muench|first=Chris|work=MSDN Blogs|publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|archive-date=2014-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140412093810/http://blogs.msdn.com/b/mikehall/archive/2005/04/26/412402.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WinSAT2005">{{Cite web|url=http://download.microsoft.com/download/9/8/f/98f3fe47-dfc3-4e74-92a3-088782200fe7/TWAR05002_WinHEC05.ppt|title=System Performance Assessment Tools for Windows 'Longhorn'|accessdate=April 18, 2015|date=2005|last=Russell|first=Richard|format=PPT|publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151105224141/http://download.microsoft.com/download/9/8/f/98f3fe47-dfc3-4e74-92a3-088782200fe7/TWAR05002_WinHEC05.ppt|archivedate=2015年11月5日}}</ref>WinSAT在发布给制造商前将是操作系统的一个开发重点。<ref name="WinSAT2006">{{Cite web|url=http://download.microsoft.com/download/5/b/9/5b97017b-e28a-4bae-ba48-174cf47d23cd/cpa101_wh06.ppt|title=Windows Vista System Requirements and WinSAT|accessdate=April 18, 2015|date=2006|last=Russell|first=Richard|format=PPT|publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]]}}</ref>

== 测试 ==
Windows Vista和Windows 7中的WinSAT执行下列测试：
* Direct3D 9 Aero评估
* Direct3D 9 Batch评估
* Direct3D 9 {{tsl|en|Alpha_compositing|Alpha Blend}}评估
* Direct3D 9 [[材质贴图|Texture]] Load评估
* Direct3D 9 [[算術邏輯單元|ALU]]评估
* Direct3D 10 Batch评估
* Direct3D 10 Alpha Blend评估
* Direct3D 10 Texture Load评估
* Direct3D 10 ALU评估
* Direct3D 10 几何评估
* Direct3D 10 固定缓冲区评估
* Windows媒体解码性能
* Windows媒体编码性能
* [[中央处理器|CPU性能]]
* [[電腦數據存貯器|内存]]性能
* [[硬盘|磁盘]]性能（包括如[[固态硬盘|固态硬盘]]的设备）
在运行期间，测试只会显示一个进度条和“工作中”的背景动画。在Vista和Windows 7中，测试期间会禁用Aero Glass以便工具能准确评估显卡和CPU。

在 Windows 7 和 Windows 8 中，WinSAT会在每周维护计划时自动运行，计划任务位置：\Microsoft\Windows\Maintenance。默认时间安排是星期日上午1时。维护计划整合各类操作系统任务到一个计划任务，以便计算机不会被各个任务随机打断。计划任务会将计算机从睡眠中唤醒，运行所有计划的任务，然后让计算机进入睡眠。在每周任务中，WinSAT会运行足够长的时间以检测是否已有任何硬件变更。如果发现，会重新运行各项测试。如果没有，WinSAT则只是自动结束并认定现有得分有效。

WinSAT在[[笔记本电脑|笔记本电脑]]使用电池供电时不会运行上述测试。

